    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points. Assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
